                         PLOT OUTLINE
.:*~*:._.:*~*:._.:*~*:._.:*~*:._.:*~*:._.:*~*:._.:*~*:._.:*~*:._.:*~*:.

Picking up where the first one leaves off, 
Light joins the task force searching for Kira 
in an effort to avert suspicion from himself...and get rid of L.

Light Yagami finds the "Death Note," a notebook with the power to kill, 
and decides to create a Utopia by killing the world&#039;s criminals, 
and soon the world&#039;s greatest detective, "L," is hired to find the perpetrator. 
An all out battle between the greatest minds on earth begins, 
the winner controlling the world.
